# Day 18 — Resend transactional email (setup link auto-send + SMTP health check).
# REST API directo (no SDK). Si RESEND_API_KEY vacío → SetupEmailService loguea
# el envío y retorna stub success (preserva flujo dev sin credentials).
# Get key from: https://resend.com/api-keys (requires verified domain)
RESEND_API_KEY=""
# Format Resend espera: "Display Name <email@verified-domain.com>"
RESEND_FROM_ADDRESS="Zenix Activate <noreply@zenix.app>"
# Base URL del cliente PMS — usado en setup link emails. Configura por env:
# - dev: http://localhost:5173
# - prod: https://app.zenix.com
APP_BASE_URL="https://app.zenix.com"
